e":{"pid":"af3392b1a2d5ed561f3b811c52a7300f7264e827","tid":2352059,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:31:10.000Z","msg":"邊個諗到環保呢個借口？明明係罷買澳洲煤造成，死要面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"就算唔關媒事，支國要做一樣野只會隔硬嚟，唔會跟其他配套。做完 create 出嚟嘅問題只會叫啲民眾接受"},{"pid":"3467995648ad1f69f3abb5726ca7156698a30408","tid":2352059,"uid":143621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國人零下四十度 冇暖氣 食草食泥 都可以生存啦"},{"pid":"578bd7065c8651a3f0ac57804835d443f69d0624","tid":2352059,"uid":340192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffcf1fdbdadda3d4c1c4b2ef8bcf3cbdfd10593","tid":2352059,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"搶完煤拎去炒賣啲领导又可以發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ec2441ccec2631a2daa879f2ca37411ffd781d","tid":2352059,"uid":380884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"你還有黨啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}